  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he took me over to the map and says, there you are.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the back of this building is a huge place with stones, like stone markers, from every village that was perished, every place in the world.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What happened in Treblinka is they didn't have a crematoria there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They had a barbecue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] When you're going to Treblinka, you'll see where the tracks stop-- the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all you'll see is, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like, grave markers, thousands of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the middle-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was not there, because if I was there, I wouldn't be here-- is a, like, a barbecue, like a block long.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At that time, they tell me-- and they have pictures of it-- that there were shelves in the barbecue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Little shelves.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They would put the people in there, in the barbecue, after they shot them, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and light the fire.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SOBBING] When the Russians were coming in, Treblinka is about 80 kilometers east of Warsaw, on the way towards Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And when the Ger-- when they were coming in, the Germans did away with everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's not-- there was not one building left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a park until the Jewish community of the world found out about it and redid it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was in the middle of the woods, and all you had was empty tracks and that's it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to speak to people in the village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke to a person who was maybe 80-- 80 something years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
